<P>Zajeer, thanks for the detailed response.&nbsp; Interesting to see a designer's point of view.</P>
<P>My biggest frustration with this zone, is like another person alluded to.&nbsp; Mob density.&nbsp; It's not easy getting folks to come here, and working this zone solo...it's difficult to make headway against the sheer number of mobs.&nbsp; Once you leave the ZI area, ever single pull involves a split.</P>
<P>I realize you didn't take this isnto account when you designed it, as it was intended as a raid zone. Anyway, thank you again for taking the time to set me straight on some things.</P>
				
